thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by Kristin

author: Kristin
title: Kristin
text: I have used American Frame for most of the art in my home. I think the website is a little awkward to use -- it's not clear exactly how to begin -- but once you get the hang of it, it's comprehensive and convenient. The frames fit together beautifully, and are well-packet to withstand the rigors of delivery.
